### ===============================================================
### HistoricalFigure API Tests (Twoje "Kategorie")
### ===============================================================

###
# [SUCCESS] Request the list of all historical figures.
GET http://localhost:9080/historyapi/api/figures/
Accept: application/json

###
# [SUCCESS] Request a single, specific figure (Napoleon).
# Używamy statycznego UUID Napoleona z repozytorium.
GET http://localhost:9080/historyapi/api/figures/15a7f9a0-7ac1-11eb-8000-0242ac110002
Accept: application/json

###
# [SUCCESS] Request a single, specific figure (Maria Curie).
# Używamy statycznego UUID Marii Curie z repozytorium.
GET http://localhost:9080/historyapi/api/figures/15a7fae0-7ac1-11eb-8001-0242ac110002
Accept: application/json

###
# [FAILURE] Request a figure with a non-existent UUID.
# To powinno zwrócić 404 Not Found.
GET http://localhost:9080/historyapi/api/figures/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
Accept: application/json

