### Note API Tests (Twoje "Elementy")
### ===============================================================

###
# [SUCCESS] Request the list of all notes.
GET http://localhost:9080/historyapi/api/notes/
Accept: application/json

###
# [SUCCESS] Request a single note by its ID.
GET http://localhost:9080/historyapi/api/notes/25b8c1f0-7ac1-11eb-8000-0242ac110002
Accept: application/json

###
